13
00:01:56,070 --> 00:01:56,640
Wanzhi!

14
00:01:56,640 --> 00:01:58,200
Another gentleman sent flower baskets!

15
00:01:58,560 --> 00:01:59,710
Two over here.

16
00:01:59,710 --> 00:02:00,710
Two over there.

17
00:02:05,790 --> 00:02:06,840
Li Xingke?

18
00:02:07,350 --> 00:02:07,870
Wanzhi!

19
00:02:08,710 --> 00:02:09,400
Congratulations.

20
00:02:10,190 --> 00:02:12,030
