21
00:02:12,560 --> 00:02:13,710
Let me see your hand.

22
00:02:14,870 --> 00:02:15,470
It's healed.

23
00:02:15,630 --> 00:02:16,560
Mr. Gao!

24
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:17,840
Emily didn't

25
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:18,470
come with you?

26
00:02:18,680 --> 00:02:19,030
No.

27
00:02:19,190 --> 00:02:20,710
I was just passing through.

28
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:22,000
Mr. Gao said

29
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:23,000
there was something big.

30
00:02:23,190 --> 00:02:24,360
So I changed my flight

31
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:25,280
and came by.

32
00:02:26,030 --> 00:02:26,520
Wanzhi,

33
00:02:26,870 --> 00:02:28,560
the store's opening
is worth celebrating.

34
00:02:29,470 --> 00:02:30,630
But isn't this business

35
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:32,360
a little small for you?

36
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:34,030
Yudan,

37
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:36,030
