38
00:02:36,630 --> 00:02:37,840
Zhao Jun, my niece.

39
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:38,960
Not me.

40
00:02:40,470 --> 00:02:41,870
Ah, looks like I misunderstood.

41
00:02:42,750 --> 00:02:44,470
I'm handling a lot more money now

42
00:02:44,470 --> 00:02:45,680
than I used to.

43
00:02:46,310 --> 00:02:47,680
But finding worthwhile investments

44
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:48,590
is the challenge.

45
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:49,520
You know,

46
00:02:49,750 --> 00:02:50,960
