47
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:52,870
Good people are hard to find.

48
00:02:53,470 --> 00:02:54,960
I trust your mind,

49
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:55,870
instincts,

50
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:56,630
and experience.

51
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:58,030
If you start

52
00:02:58,030 --> 00:02:58,840
a business,

53
00:02:59,190 --> 00:02:59,800
please give us

54
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:00,630
