55
00:03:01,630 --> 00:03:02,520
Sure, Mr. Li.

56
00:03:02,710 --> 00:03:04,000
I look forward to your support.

57
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:10,560
Zhao Jun.

58
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:11,710
Xingke is here.

59
00:03:11,870 --> 00:03:12,560
Welcome!

60
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:13,360
Ms. Zhao!

61
00:03:13,870 --> 00:03:14,430
Take a look.

62
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:16,630
Pretty impressive, right?

63
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:17,750
The speakers are ready.

64
00:03:17,910 --> 00:03:18,400
Okay.

65
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:20,030
Fang Wanzhi.

66
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:21,150
Come here.

67
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:22,430
Mr. He,

68
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:23,240
pause for a sec.

69
00:03:23,710 --> 00:03:25,030
I've got some great news.

70
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:26,470
Coming!

71
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:29,680
Regarding Zhao Jun's work injury,

72
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:31,910
the department took it very seriously.

73
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,560
The factory has already

74
00:03:33,590 --> 00:03:34,800
met with me.

75
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:36,280
They admitted fault

76
00:03:36,310 --> 00:03:37,280
