77
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:38,190
Just now,

78
00:03:38,430 --> 00:03:40,360
they presented a new
settlement proposal.

79
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:43,430
The compensation is substantial.

80
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:45,360
Now it's up to us whether we agree.

81
00:03:45,430 --> 00:03:46,400
No agreement.

82
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:52,240
Neither of you agrees?

83
00:03:53,310 --> 00:03:53,910
Fang Wanzhi,

84
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:54,750
you didn't even ask

85
00:03:54,750 --> 00:03:55,750
