428
00:14:12,080 --> 00:14:12,910
Let me walk you out.

429
00:14:12,910 --> 00:14:13,910
(Let's go.)

430
00:14:13,910 --> 00:14:14,440
(Mr. Xu.)

431
00:14:14,840 --> 00:14:15,840
(Let's stay in touch.)

432
00:14:15,840 --> 00:14:17,000
(Of course.)

433
00:14:18,360 --> 00:14:19,150
See you next time.

434
00:14:19,150 --> 00:14:20,000
See you.

435
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:20,630
Take care.

436
00:14:20,630 --> 00:14:21,030
Sure.

437
00:14:21,150 --> 00:14:21,840
Bye, Mr. Xu.

438
00:14:21,910 --> 00:14:22,550
Goodbye.

439
00:14:22,600 --> 00:14:23,480
Mr. Gold Tooth.

440
00:14:23,480 --> 00:14:24,510
I'm off.

441
00:14:24,910 --> 00:14:25,720
You were a huge help.

442
00:14:26,240 --> 00:14:26,790
Happy to help.

443
00:14:26,790 --> 00:14:27,630
Watch your step!

444
00:14:27,630 --> 00:14:28,270
Bye, Mr. Xu!

445
00:14:28,320 --> 00:14:28,790
Bye!

446
00:14:34,320 --> 00:14:34,840
Qian.

447
00:14:44,270 --> 00:14:45,510
I spotted you a while ago.

448
00:14:46,720 --> 00:14:47,550
With Gao Xiang.

449
00:14:48,910 --> 00:14:49,480
That's good.

450
00:14:49,910 --> 00:14:50,960
You've got skills.

451
00:14:51,960 --> 00:14:52,750
Mr. Gold Tooth

452
00:14:53,000 --> 00:14:53,720
and Mr. Xu.

453
00:14:54,600 --> 00:14:55,390
They are

454
00:14:55,390 --> 00:14:56,600
my clients now.

455
00:14:57,030 --> 00:14:58,240
I thought their businesses

456
00:14:58,240 --> 00:14:59,200
might be a good fit.

457
00:14:59,200 --> 00:15:00,150
So I introduced them.

458
00:15:00,550 --> 00:15:02,030
Didn't expect it to work.

459
00:15:02,320 --> 00:15:04,870
And they both support my work.

460
00:15:05,120 --> 00:15:06,150
What do you do now?

461
00:15:06,600 --> 00:15:07,510
Insurance.

462
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:08,790
Oh, Wanzhi,

463
00:15:08,840 --> 00:15:10,240
