464
00:15:10,910 --> 00:15:13,360
A policy brings peace of mind.

465
00:15:13,720 --> 00:15:15,840
It shields you from life's storms.

466
00:15:16,000 --> 00:15:18,790
A safety net for the future.

467
00:15:19,320 --> 00:15:22,120
A way to care for yourself.

468
00:15:24,080 --> 00:15:25,240
Are you pitching me?

469
00:15:25,550 --> 00:15:26,870
Of course not!

470
00:15:27,080 --> 00:15:28,320
I'll give you one.

471
00:15:28,550 --> 00:15:29,870
With critical illness insurance.

472
00:15:30,360 --> 00:15:31,320
And one for Juan.

473
00:15:31,550 --> 00:15:32,750
I'll cover both of you.

474
00:15:33,320 --> 00:15:34,720
Looks like you're doing well.

475
00:15:36,910 --> 00:15:38,600
Most importantly,

476
00:15:40,320 --> 00:15:41,630
I don't have to

477
00:15:42,270 --> 00:15:43,600
rely on men.

478
00:15:48,670 --> 00:15:49,600
Feels so good!

479
00:15:50,600 --> 00:15:51,670
I've held onto these words

480
00:15:51,670 --> 00:15:52,480
for so long.

481
00:15:52,840 --> 00:15:54,240
If I hadn't run into you,

482
00:15:54,240 --> 00:15:55,550
I would've said it.

483
00:15:56,200 --> 00:15:58,030
Wanzhi, I missed you so much.

484
00:16:09,750 --> 00:16:10,320
You should

485
00:16:10,360 --> 00:16:11,720
sell insurance too.

486
00:16:12,080 --> 00:16:13,200
This industry

487
00:16:13,200 --> 00:16:14,510
has a bright future.

488
00:16:15,440 --> 00:16:16,120
Just show

489
00:16:16,150 --> 00:16:18,030
your smile,

490
00:16:18,240 --> 00:16:19,750
and you'll get a lot of clients.

491
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:20,670
I'm telling you.

492
00:16:20,960 --> 00:16:22,200
Every policy pays.

493
00:16:22,440 --> 00:16:23,150
Way better

494
00:16:23,150 --> 00:16:24,440
than being an assistant.

495
00:16:25,080 --> 00:16:26,630
Oh, you quit.

496
00:16:26,840 --> 00:16:28,320
Perfect. Let me get you started.

497
00:16:28,550 --> 00:16:29,870
How did you know I quit?

498
00:16:32,630 --> 00:16:33,600
Uh...

499
00:16:35,030 --> 00:16:36,840
I've been secretly

500
00:16:37,840 --> 00:16:39,670
keeping up with you two.

501
00:16:40,120 --> 00:16:41,120
Why on the low?

502
00:16:41,720 --> 00:16:42,750
I was ashamed.

503
00:16:44,390 --> 00:16:46,240
That situation got really ugly.

504
00:16:46,240 --> 00:16:47,320
Without your brother,

505
00:16:48,870 --> 00:16:50,720
it would have been worse.

506
00:16:51,550 --> 00:16:52,270
Wanzhi,

507
00:16:53,120 --> 00:16:53,910
thank you.

508
00:16:54,150 --> 00:16:55,120
You took

509
00:16:55,120 --> 00:16:56,870
that knife for me.

510
00:16:58,080 --> 00:16:59,840
I'll never forget it.

511
00:17:00,480 --> 00:17:01,480
Then let's stay in touch.

512
00:17:02,150 --> 00:17:02,750
Meet up more.

513
00:17:05,270 --> 00:17:06,640
I knew it!

514
00:17:06,640 --> 00:17:08,640
I knew you wouldn't hate me.

515
00:17:11,830 --> 00:17:13,160
We said it a long time ago.

516
00:17:14,030 --> 00:17:15,160
Friends for life.

517
00:17:16,400 --> 00:17:17,310
Wanzhi.

518
00:17:35,510 --> 00:17:37,640
What a beautiful receipt.

519
00:17:41,750 --> 00:17:43,550
Seventy-seven, instant noodles.

520
00:17:46,240 --> 00:17:47,880
Not bad.

521
00:17:50,110 --> 00:17:52,000
Profits are better than I thought.

522
00:17:53,310 --> 00:17:53,830
Zhao Jun,

523
00:17:54,350 --> 00:17:55,550
your aunt is gonna

524
00:17:55,550 --> 00:17:56,480
start a toy factory.

525
00:17:56,550 --> 00:17:58,350
She's recruiting now.

526
00:17:58,550 --> 00:17:59,480
With this supermarket,

527
00:17:59,480 --> 00:18:00,270
