528
00:18:00,270 --> 00:18:01,350
Don't regret it.

529
00:18:02,160 --> 00:18:03,000
I won't regret it.

530
00:18:03,240 --> 00:18:04,070
I could help with

531
00:18:04,310 --> 00:18:05,550
the toy factory too.

532
00:18:05,920 --> 00:18:07,440
Can I put my cut

533
00:18:07,550 --> 00:18:08,590
from the supermarket

534
00:18:08,680 --> 00:18:09,590
into the factory?

535
00:18:10,350 --> 00:18:12,400
What a clever girl!

536
00:18:12,790 --> 00:18:14,350
You wanna

537
00:18:14,350 --> 00:18:15,790
be a founding shareholder?

538
00:18:16,200 --> 00:18:17,750
You've got both sides covered!

539
00:18:17,750 --> 00:18:19,400
Night school really paid off.

540
00:18:20,750 --> 00:18:21,440
Auntie,

541
00:18:22,070 --> 00:18:23,640
I got my associate degree.

542
00:18:23,960 --> 00:18:24,790
Really?

543
00:18:25,480 --> 00:18:26,590
Congratulations!

544
00:18:27,960 --> 00:18:29,270
How's he doing?

545
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:31,510
Grandpa?

546
00:18:32,550 --> 00:18:33,240
He's doing great.

547
00:18:33,960 --> 00:18:36,110
He takes over after midnight.

548
00:18:36,350 --> 00:18:37,680
I really feel for him.

549
00:18:38,830 --> 00:18:40,200
But he says being old means

550
00:18:40,240 --> 00:18:40,880
less sleep

551
00:18:41,110 --> 00:18:42,270
and insists on the late shift.

552
00:18:42,880 --> 00:18:44,200
He's sharp with the books.

553
00:18:44,440 --> 00:18:45,160
Never slips up.

554
00:18:45,640 --> 00:18:46,680
The customers like him.

555
00:18:47,110 --> 00:18:48,920
They call him the Old Man
from Shenxian Peak.

556
00:18:49,960 --> 00:18:50,960
Did he smoke?

557
00:18:53,480 --> 00:18:54,030
No.

558
00:18:55,720 --> 00:18:56,350
Zhao Jun,

559
00:18:56,960 --> 00:18:57,960
protecting your grandpa

560
00:18:57,960 --> 00:18:59,550
means losing the investors' trust.

561
00:19:00,270 --> 00:19:01,350
Still, that's filial.

562
00:19:01,480 --> 00:19:01,960
No.

563
00:19:02,200 --> 00:19:03,510
He didn't smoke openly.

564
00:19:04,200 --> 00:19:04,960
So, on the sly?

565
00:19:05,070 --> 00:19:06,350
I don't know.

566
00:19:07,000 --> 00:19:07,720
However,

567
00:19:07,830 --> 00:19:09,240
three packs are missing.

568
00:19:09,350 --> 00:19:10,110
Three packs!

569
00:19:10,590 --> 00:19:11,480
But I really don't know

570
00:19:11,480 --> 00:19:12,550
