571
00:19:18,550 --> 00:19:19,070
Mr. He,

572
00:19:19,400 --> 00:19:20,000
let's talk.

573
00:19:20,400 --> 00:19:20,960
Wanzhi...

574
00:19:26,030 --> 00:19:27,310
I was dozing off.

575
00:19:28,200 --> 00:19:29,350
What's wrong?

576
00:19:30,110 --> 00:19:30,880
Gao Xiang explained

577
00:19:30,880 --> 00:19:32,110
