578
00:19:32,310 --> 00:19:33,110
Yeah.

579
00:19:33,400 --> 00:19:34,240
You're fired.

580
00:19:34,590 --> 00:19:35,550
Pay a penalty

581
00:19:35,550 --> 00:19:36,550
