586
00:19:42,400 --> 00:19:43,590
Why is there a penalty?

587
00:19:43,750 --> 00:19:45,640
You... you must be scamming me!

588
00:19:45,790 --> 00:19:46,960
You smoked.

589
00:19:47,200 --> 00:19:47,920
No!

590
00:19:48,070 --> 00:19:49,240
Three packs are missing.

591
00:19:49,480 --> 00:19:51,110
I have to be honest.

592
00:19:51,400 --> 00:19:52,240
Can't cover for you.

593
00:19:52,680 --> 00:19:53,720
No... I...

594
00:19:53,750 --> 00:19:54,880
I didn't smoke.

595
00:19:54,920 --> 00:19:56,200
Then why are three packs missing?

596
00:19:56,270 --> 00:19:57,590
I never mess up inventory.

597
00:19:57,790 --> 00:19:58,200
That...

598
00:19:58,400 --> 00:19:59,550
If you did it, just own it.

599
00:19:59,550 --> 00:20:00,790
She's just worried about you.

600
00:20:01,160 --> 00:20:02,200
- The doctor said...
- Juan.

601
00:20:02,640 --> 00:20:03,310
Stay out of it.

602
00:20:03,640 --> 00:20:04,550
Go help at the store.

603
00:20:09,440 --> 00:20:10,110
Uh, this...

604
00:20:11,920 --> 00:20:13,440
I didn't smoke.

605
00:20:13,680 --> 00:20:14,440
Grandpa,

606
00:20:14,880 --> 00:20:16,270
you're the one in the wrong.

607
00:20:16,960 --> 00:20:18,270
